            "description": "Dallas-based organization Housing Solutions for North Texas (DHA) has received approval for a $69 million bond reservation. This funding will be used for the development activities of the Roseland Townhomes and Roseland Estates, historic affordable housing properties in Central Dallas. The Texas Bond Review Board (BRB) has approved a total reservation of $69,152,737. This financing milestone allows DHA to move forward with renovations on 274 housing units.",
